ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada – China ** Sharing and Return of Forfeited Assets **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT ON SHARING AND RETURN OF FORFEITED ASSETS between the Government of Canada and the Government of the PEOPLE’S REPUBLIC OF CHINA.
